title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/readme

! JSON Convert

A general-purpose JSON-to-tiddler converter, with reusable
profiles, a staging area for preview and collision resolution, and
tolerant input handling.

* Open the [[Console|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/Console]] to paste source JSON, pick a profile, and run a conversion.
* Manage profiles in the [[Editor|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/Editor]] — launched from the Console's ''Edit'' / ''New…'' buttons.
* Profiles are tiddlers tagged `$:/tags/json-convert/profile`.  Custom transforms are tiddlers tagged `$:/tags/json-convert/transform` (JavaScript or wikitext bodies, `value` in scope).

Version: <$transclude tiddler="$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert" field="version"/>
